  "text": "Protein concentrations were determined as described by Read and Northcote [CITATION_1] using bovine serum albumin (Sigma-Aldrich Chem. Co., St. Louis, MO, USA) as standard. Total neutral carbohydrates were quantified by the method described by Dubois et al. [CITATION_2] , using mannose as standard.",
